@123181 = ~Minor Spell Deflection~
//
@12318 = ~Minor Spell Deflection
Level: 3
School: Abjuration
Range: Personal
Duration: 5 turns
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None

This abjuration causes any spells directed at the caster to be absorbed and consumed. This affects a total of 4 spell levels, meaning it can absorb four 1st-level spells or one spell of 4th level or higher. Having one 'spell level' of protection left means a 1st level spell would get absorbed, as well as a 9th level spell. This spell will also protect the caster from Dispel/Remove Magic and Breach, while its protection lasts.

This spell absorbs magic effects cast from most scrolls and innate spell-like abilities, but will not protect against stationary area-effect spells such as Cloudkill or Stinking Cloud.
~
