@12513 = ~Breach
Level: 5
School: Abjuration
Range: Long
Duration: Instant
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: None

When this spell is cast at a creature, it breaches and dispels all of the 'specific protections' and 'combat protections' on the target creature. The target's Magic Resistance, if any, does not affect this spell.

The 'specific protections' dispelled by Breach include spells such as: Chaos Shield, Resist Fear, Spirit Ward, Spiritual Clarity, Chaotic Commands, Death Ward, Divine Protection, Emotion: Hope, Exaltation, Free Action, Impervious Sanctity of Mind, Mind Blank, Mirrored Eyes, Protection from Acid, Protection from Cold, Protection from Fire, Protection from Electricity, Protection from the Elements, Resist Elements, Protection from Divination, Protection from Energy, Protection from Magic Energy, Storm Shell, and Storm Shield. 

The 'combat protections' dispelled by Breach include spells such as: Armor, Shield, Spirit Armor, Armor of Faith, Barkskin, Stoneskin, Iron Skin, Protection from Normal Weapons, Protection from Magical Weapons, Protection from Missiles, Physical Mirror, Circle of Bones, Cloak of Darkness, Emotion: Courage, Fire Shield, Acid Sheath, Moment of Prescience, and Absolute Immunity.~
